                <p class="text-justify">Everyone has their dream destination. Travelling is one of the best things to try in this life. Taking a small break from daily boring lives is crucial to stay well in the long term. Earth has beautiful places to explore. The beauty of these places is incomparable. Below we will discuss the top 8 places to visit and create the best memories. </p>


                <h2>Machu Picchu, Peru</h2>
                <p class="text-justify">Machu Picchu is located in the high altitudes of the Andes mountains. The site has been abandoned for nearly 100 years, but it amazes and attracts tourists with its perfectly joined, intricate stonework. </p>

                <p class="text-justify">Enormous-sized multi-ton blocks of stone are perfectly joined without any cement or mortar. The journey to Machu Picchu starts from the mountain city of Cusco. Cusco is a fantastic place to explore and spend a few days before or after your journey to Machu Picchu. </p>

                <p class="text-justify">One can hike from Cusco to Machu Picchu. The total time needed to hike is around five days. Steps have been taken to avoid over-tourism. The number of visitors at a time has also been reduced. </p>


                <h2>Grand Canyon, Arizona</h2>
                <p class="text-justify">The Grand Canyon is among one of the seven wonders of the world. The Canyon is around 18 miles wide in places. The South Rim of the Grand Canyon is a major tourist attraction spot. Here several impressive hikes in to the Grand Canyon begin. </p>

                <p class="text-justify">Great overlooks are spread along the rim road, also known as the Desert View Drive. Many accommodations are available here, from tents to luxurious resorts built from logs. The North rim also has a few accommodations. </p>

                <p class="text-justify">The Canyon can also be accessed through the Grand Canyon Railway. The rail line is around 64 miles and provides an entertaining and adventurous way to get inside the Canyon with food and music. The Grand Canyon is one of the <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/blog/travel-guide-top-places-visit-in-2022.aspx">best places to travel in the world</a> according to most people. </p>


                <h3>Istanbul, Turkey</h3>
                <p class="text-justify">Istanbul is a beautiful destination where one can find a mix of culture, food, and history. One can spend their day shopping in the malls and at night have a beautiful experience at a wonderful restaurant eating delicious turkey food and then rise in the morning to the sound of Ezan. Istanbul has excellent public transit. </p>

                <p class="text-justify">One can easily get around and explore major sites and monuments. One must explore the Blue Mosque, Hagia Sofia, and the Topkapi Palace. </p>

                <p class="text-justify">The Gulhane Park in Istanbul is one of the largest public parks in the Sultanahmet. The park has pathways, flower beds, and a pool. It is an attractive spot. One can relax on the park bench and get a beautiful view of the Bosphorus, Sea of Marmara, and Princes' Islands from the park's northeastern corner. </p>


                <h3>Maui, Hawaii</h3>
                <p class="text-justify">Hawaii Island provides a lifetime experience to its visitors. One can surf and enjoy meals while sitting near the beach. Horse riding is also provided across the dormant volcano in the Haleakala National Park. </p>

                <p class="text-justify">One can also go on an adventurous hike through a rainforest in the West Maui Mountains. The island's natural scenery makes it one of the best travel destinations in 2022. </p>

                <p class="text-justify">Tourists can accommodate rustic hippie bungalow beds and breakfasts. They can also stay in five-star luxury resort hotels. All luxurious hotels are present in Wailea. One should try to spend some time venturing out in Kihei. </p>

                <p class="text-justify">It is a popular place where the locals hang out. To get <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/flights/san-francisco-sfo-to-maui-ogg-flights.aspx">cheap flights to Maui</a>, try booking plane ticket fees days before departure from sites like Skyscanner, Google Flights, and many more. </p>


                <h4>Rome, Italy</h4>
                <p class="text-justify">Rome is on the wishlist of most people. If you visit Rome, you must explore the Colosseum and adjacent Roman Forum, the Pantheon, and Vatican City. Explore the outskirts of Rome as well. Hiking along with a tomb-lined section of the Appian Way, the ancient Roman superhighway will give you a bucket full of memories. Try to visit the ruins outside the city as well. </p>

                <p class="text-justify">Rome has a beautiful assortment of beach towns on the Lazio coast. You can take a bath in the cool waters of the Tyrrhenian Sea. April and May are the best time to visit Rome since the weather is pleasant and you will get a fair airfare deal. </p>


                <h4>Taj Mahal, India</h4>
                <p class="text-justify">You must visit the Taj Mahal once in your lifetime. It is one of the Seven Wonders of the world. Taj Mahal symbols pure, true, and never-ending love. Contrary to popular belief, the Taj Mahal is not a palace but the final resting place of Mumtaz Mahal, built by Shah Jahan. It is one of the finest Mughal architecture and has four identical sides over its 240-foot height. </p>

                <p class="text-justify">You can notice its appearance shifting slightly throughout the day with sunlight. You can also see its reflection in the huge pool beneath it. Try strolling and spending some time in the large garden outside for a magnificent experience. You can also visit the Agra Fort near the Taj Mahal. It is a UNESCO world heritage site. </p>


                <h5>Paris, France</h5>
                <p class="text-justify">Paris, also known as the City of Lights, is one of the best vacation spots for couples. The ambiance and the energy of this Parisian destination attract couples from around the world. One will find themselves mesmerized by the coffee shops, perfect-sized cobblestone streets, and scent of fresh bakeries perfuming the air. You can spend days exploring the Eiffel Tower and Pont Des Arts Bridge outside Notre Dame. </p>

                <p class="text-justify">Consider renting bikes if you visit Paris in spring, summer, or fall. Tour through the museums, which feature classic and modern themes. Cheap flights to Paris are available from late November till March. </p>


                <h5>Venice, Italy</h5>
                <p class="text-justify">Venice is another best vacation spot for couples. Venice presents an entirely new experience. It comprises 100 tiny islands. There are few roads but many canals; therefore, you must take a gondola ride. </p>

                <p class="text-justify">Do not miss exploring the Rialto Bridge. Go to St Mark's Square, where local vendors display their handmade goods. Hundreds of pigeons swarm this area in search of tasty treats; hence try to hold your food tight. </p>

                <p class="text-justify">The top of Campanile Bell Tower offers the best view of the city. Take a boat ride to the glass-blowing region on Murano Island. The <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/">airline reservations</a> to Venice are cheap from November to March. </p>




